==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: chemosorption
<hw>chemosorption</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>adsorption (especially when
irreversible) by means of chemical instead of physical forces; <as>as,
<ex>chemosorption</ex> of gaseous nitrogen on iron
catalysts</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> chemisorption.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

